---
id: org.dxos.plugin.versioning
name: VersioningPlugin
version: 0.1.0
---

A generic version/review plugin for DXOS Composer. Adds a history companion (checkpoints, branches,
merges) to any object type that opts in via a HistoryProvider, plus per-user version selection and
review-mode state and a default review-render policy.

## Extensions

The following extension dialects are used in this document.

| Term        | URI                            |
|-------------|--------------------------------|
| `type`      | `org.dxos.mdl.type@1.0`       |
| `feat`      | `org.dxos.mdl.feat@1.0`       |
| `component` | `org.dxos.mdl.component@1.0`  |

## Types

```mdl
type VersionSelection
  literals: current | branch | fork | checkpoint
  desc: Which version of an object the local user is viewing. Never replicated.
```

```mdl
type ReviewMode
  literals: editing | suggesting | viewing
  desc: Per-user editing posture for a document. Local UI preference, never replicated.
```

```mdl
type HistoryProvider
  fields:
    id: string                  # typename gating the history companion
    getTarget: Function         # resolves the versioned Text root for an object
  desc: Per-type opt-in to the generic history companion.
```

## Components

```mdl
component ObjectHistory
  desc: |
    Companion panel: git-graph timeline of an object's checkpoints, branch forks, and merges.
    Clicking a checkpoint time-travels the object's surfaces; clicking a branch fork switches to it.
    Gated per-type by a HistoryProvider contribution.
  props:
    subject: History.VersionedObject
    role?: string
  actions:
    createCheckpoint(name)
    createBranch(name)
    merge()
    discard()
```

## Features

```mdl
feat F-1: History Companion

  req F-1.1:
    when: an object's typename has a registered HistoryProvider
    then: the object gains a companion "History" node in the app graph
  req F-1.2:
    when: user selects a checkpoint in the timeline
    then: the object's surfaces time-travel to that revision (per-user, not replicated)
```

```mdl
feat F-2: Review Model

  req F-2.1: A default review-render policy maps review mode to render config with GDocs parity.
  req F-2.2:
    when: a plugin contributes a ReviewRenderPolicy earlier in plugin order
    then: that policy overrides the default
```

## Appendix: Extension Definitions

```mdl
ext type
  uri: org.dxos.mdl.type@1.0
  desc: A named data structure with typed fields and optional literals.
  fields:
    desc?: Prose
    fields?: FieldMap
    literals?: UnionList
```

```mdl
ext feat
  uri: org.dxos.mdl.feat@1.0
  desc: A named feature grouping one or more requirements.
  fields:
    desc?: Prose
    req: RequirementList
  nesting: self
```

```mdl
ext component
  uri: org.dxos.mdl.component@1.0
  desc: A UI component with props, internal state, slots, actions, and events.
  fields:
    desc?: Prose
    props?: FieldMap
    state?: FieldMap
    slots?: FieldMap
    actions?: ActionMap
```
